tinymce.Resource.add("tinymce.html-i18n.help-keynav.tr",`<h1>Klavyeyle gezintiyi ba\u015Flatma</h1>

<dl>
  <dt>Men\xFC \xE7ubu\u011Funa odaklan</dt>
  <dd>Windows veya Linux: Alt+F9</dd>
  <dd>macOS: &#x2325;F9</dd>
  <dt>Ara\xE7 \xE7ubu\u011Funa odaklan</dt>
  <dd>Windows veya Linux: Alt+F10</dd>
  <dd>macOS: &#x2325;F10</dd>
  <dt>Alt bilgiye odaklan</dt>
  <dd>Windows veya Linux: Alt+F11</dd>
  <dd>macOS: &#x2325;F11</dd>
  <dt>Bildirime odakla</dt>
  <dd>Windows veya Linux: Alt+F12</dd>
  <dd>macOS: &#x2325;F12</dd>
  <dt>Ba\u011Flamsal ara\xE7 \xE7ubu\u011Funa odaklan</dt>
  <dd>Windows, Linux veya macOS: Ctrl+F9</dd>
</dl>

<p>Gezinti ilk kullan\u0131c\u0131 arabirimi \xF6\u011Fesinden ba\u015Flar, bu \xF6\u011Fe vurgulan\u0131r ya da ilk \xF6\u011Fe, Alt bilgi eleman\u0131
  yolundaysa alt\u0131 \xE7izilir.</p>

<h1>Kullan\u0131c\u0131 arabirimi b\xF6l\xFCmleri aras\u0131nda gezinme</h1>

<p>Sonraki kullan\u0131c\u0131 arabirimi b\xF6l\xFCm\xFCne gitmek i\xE7in <strong>Sekme</strong> tu\u015Funa bas\u0131n.</p>

<p>\xD6nceki kullan\u0131c\u0131 arabirimi b\xF6l\xFCm\xFCne gitmek i\xE7in <strong>Shift+Sekme</strong> tu\u015Flar\u0131na bas\u0131n.</p>

<p>Bu kullan\u0131c\u0131 arabirimi b\xF6l\xFCmlerinin <strong>Sekme</strong> s\u0131ras\u0131:</p>

<ol>
  <li>Men\xFC \xE7ubu\u011Fu</li>
  <li>Her ara\xE7 \xE7ubu\u011Fu grubu</li>
  <li>Kenar \xE7ubu\u011Fu</li>
  <li>Alt bilgide \xF6\u011Fe yolu</li>
  <li>Alt bilgide s\xF6zc\xFCk say\u0131s\u0131 ge\xE7i\u015F d\xFC\u011Fmesi</li>
  <li>Alt bilgide marka ba\u011Flant\u0131s\u0131</li>
  <li>Alt bilgide d\xFCzenleyiciyi yeniden boyutland\u0131rma tutamac\u0131</li>
</ol>

<p>Kullan\u0131c\u0131 arabirimi b\xF6l\xFCm\xFC yoksa atlan\u0131r.</p>

<p>Alt bilgide klavyeyle gezinti oda\u011F\u0131 yoksa ve g\xF6r\xFCn\xFCr bir kenar \xE7ubu\u011Fu mevcut de\u011Filse <strong>Shift+Sekme</strong> tu\u015Flar\u0131na bas\u0131ld\u0131\u011F\u0131nda
  odak son ara\xE7 \xE7ubu\u011Fu yerine ilk ara\xE7 \xE7ubu\u011Fu grubuna ta\u015F\u0131n\u0131r.</p>

<h1>Kullan\u0131c\u0131 arabirimi b\xF6l\xFCmleri i\xE7inde gezinme</h1>

<p>Sonraki kullan\u0131c\u0131 arabirimi eleman\u0131na gitmek i\xE7in uygun <strong>Ok</strong> tu\u015Funa bas\u0131n.</p>

<p><strong>Sol</strong> ve <strong>Sa\u011F</strong> ok tu\u015Flar\u0131</p>

<ul>
  <li>men\xFC \xE7ubu\u011Fundaki men\xFCler aras\u0131nda hareket eder.</li>
  <li>men\xFCde bir alt men\xFC a\xE7ar.</li>
  <li>ara\xE7 \xE7ubu\u011Fu grubundaki d\xFC\u011Fmeler aras\u0131nda hareket eder.</li>
  <li>alt bilginin \xF6\u011Fe yolundaki \xF6\u011Feler aras\u0131nda hareket eder.</li>
</ul>

<p><strong>A\u015Fa\u011F\u0131</strong> ve <strong>Yukar\u0131</strong> ok tu\u015Flar\u0131</p>

<ul>
  <li>men\xFCdeki men\xFC \xF6\u011Feleri aras\u0131nda hareket eder.</li>
  <li>ara\xE7 \xE7ubu\u011Fu a\xE7\u0131l\u0131r men\xFCs\xFCndeki \xF6\u011Feler aras\u0131nda hareket eder.</li>
</ul>

<p><strong>Ok</strong> tu\u015Flar\u0131, odaklan\u0131lan kullan\u0131c\u0131 arabirimi b\xF6l\xFCm\xFC i\xE7inde d\xF6ng\xFCsel olarak hareket eder.</p>

<p>A\xE7\u0131k bir men\xFCy\xFC, a\xE7\u0131k bir alt men\xFCy\xFC veya a\xE7\u0131k bir a\xE7\u0131l\u0131r men\xFCy\xFC kapatmak i\xE7in <strong>Esc</strong> tu\u015Funa bas\u0131n.</p>

<p>Ge\xE7erli odak belirli bir kullan\u0131c\u0131 arabirimi b\xF6l\xFCm\xFCn\xFCn "\xFCst" k\u0131sm\u0131ndaysa <strong>Esc</strong> tu\u015Funa bas\u0131ld\u0131\u011F\u0131nda
  klavyeyle gezintiden de tamamen \xE7\u0131k\u0131l\u0131r.</p>

<h1>Men\xFC \xF6\u011Fesini veya ara\xE7 \xE7ubu\u011Fu d\xFC\u011Fmesini y\xFCr\xFCtme</h1>

<p>\u0130stedi\u011Finiz men\xFC \xF6\u011Fesi veya ara\xE7 \xE7ubu\u011Fu d\xFC\u011Fmesi vurguland\u0131\u011F\u0131nda <strong>Return</strong>, <strong>Enter</strong>
  veya <strong>Ara \xE7ubu\u011Fu</strong> tu\u015Funa bas\u0131n.</p>

<h1>Sekme bulunmayan ileti\u015Fim kutular\u0131nda gezinme</h1>

<p>Sekme bulunmayan ileti\u015Fim kutular\u0131nda, ileti\u015Fim kutusu a\xE7\u0131ld\u0131\u011F\u0131nda ilk etkile\u015Fimli bile\u015Fene odaklan\u0131l\u0131r.</p>

<p>Etkile\u015Fimli ileti\u015Fim kutusu bile\u015Fenleri aras\u0131nda gezinmek i\xE7in <strong>Sekme</strong> veya <strong>Shift+ Sekme</strong> tu\u015Flar\u0131na bas\u0131n.</p>

<h1>Sekmeli ileti\u015Fim kutular\u0131nda gezinme</h1>

<p>Sekmeli ileti\u015Fim kutular\u0131nda, ileti\u015Fim kutusu a\xE7\u0131ld\u0131\u011F\u0131nda sekme men\xFCs\xFCndeki ilk d\xFC\u011Fmeye odaklan\u0131l\u0131r.</p>

<p>Bu ileti\u015Fim kutusu sekmesinin etkile\u015Fimli bile\u015Fenleri aras\u0131nda gezinmek i\xE7in <strong>Sekme</strong> veya
  <strong>Shift+Sekme</strong> tu\u015Flar\u0131na bas\u0131n.</p>

<p>Mevcut sekmeler aras\u0131nda ge\xE7i\u015F yapmak i\xE7in sekme men\xFCs\xFCne odaklan\u0131p uygun <strong>Ok</strong> tu\u015Funa basarak
  ba\u015Fka bir ileti\u015Fim kutusu sekmesine ge\xE7i\u015F yap\u0131n.</p>
`);
